OL,5,Cburdens
OL,7,FAlmost four months on from the crash,
OL,8,Fand as Vishwashkumar Ramesh limped
OL,9,Finto his seat for our interview, it
OL,10,Fwas clear that although time has
OL,11,Fpassed, his pain is as raw as the day
OL,12,Fit happened.
OL,14,FVishwash is the sole survivor of Air
OL,15,FIndia 171, which crashed 32 seconds
OL,16,Fafter takeoff on June 12, 2025.
OL,18,FHe had been in India helping his
OL,19,Fbrother, Ajay, with their fishing
OL,20,Fbusiness, and they were both on the
OL,21,Fsame flight home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
