OL,7,FDuring takeoff, the Boeing 787
OL,8,FDreamliner lost altitude and crashed
OL,9,Finto the BJ Medical College in
OL,10,FAhmedabad.
OL,12,FIn total, 241 people on board died -
OL,13,F168 Indian nationals and 53 British
OL,14,Fpeople. On the ground, a further 19
OL,15,Fpeople were killed and 67 were injured.
OL,17,FAs smoke billowed out of the
OL,18,Fsurrounding buildings, Vishwash,
OL,19,Fwearing one shoe and covered in blood,
OL,20,Fmiraculously walked away and tried to
OL,21,Fphone his father back in Leicester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
