OL,7,FWitnesses at the time said Vishwash
OL,8,Ftried to find his brother when he
OL,9,Frealised what had happened, but Ajay
OL,10,Fnever made it off the plane.
OL,12,FAs we started talking about that day,
OL,13,FVishwash kept talking about the loss
OL,14,Fof his brother and the life he and his
OL,15,Ffamily once lived.
OL,17,FSpeaking of his life now, he said:
OL,18,F"It's completely different, after this
OL,19,Ftragedy - physically, mentally, I lost
OL,20,Fmy younger brother. My whole family
OL,21,Fbroke down, completely.
