OL,7,F"In the last four months, I'm not
OL,8,Ftalking with my friends, my family."
OL,10,FVishwash managed to escape the
OL,11,Fwreckage by crawling out through a gap
OL,12,Fnear a broken emergency exit door.
OL,13,FSocial media clips at the time showed
OL,14,Fhim walking down the street in the
OL,15,Fimmediate aftermath.
OL,17,FVishwash has a four-year-old son, whom
OL,18,Fhe also said he does not talk too much.
OL,20,F"I'm just alone, living in my room,
OL,21,Fsitting on my bed.
