OL,7,F"He likes to spend time with me, but
OL,8,FI'm not giving time to him because
OL,9,Fmentally, I'm completely..." Vishwash
OL,10,Fisn't able to finish the thought.
OL,12,FAfter meeting his family on the day of
OL,13,Fthe crash, I have been regularly
OL,14,Fspeaking with those closest to the
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,FThroughout that time, we have
OL,18,Fdiscussed Vishwash's health and when
OL,19,Fhe might want to speak to the media
OL,20,Fabout what happened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
