OL,7,FVishwash said he is not only suffering
OL,8,Fphysically but also mentally, leaving
OL,9,Fhim in a state of loneliness
OL,11,FVishwash believes that the time is
OL,12,Fnow, because he says he needs more
OL,13,Fsupport from Air India.
OL,15,FDuring our interview, Vishwash was
OL,16,Fsitting between his community leader
OL,17,Fand family adviser, Sanjiv Patel, and
OL,18,Flegal adviser, Radd Seiger, both there
OL,19,Fto help guide him through what he
OL,20,Fwanted to say.
