OL,7,FI asked Vishwash how it felt when
OL,8,Fpeople called him a miracle. He
OL,9,Fresponded: "It feels good, but at the
OL,10,Fsame time, I lost my brother in the
OL,11,Fsame flight."
OL,13,FWhat became quickly clear was that
OL,14,FVishwash is still in pain. After
OL,15,Fanswering some questions, he would
OL,16,Foften lean back in the chair to try
OL,17,Fand stretch his right knee, which he
OL,18,Fsays still hurts him every day.
