OL,7,FVishwash said he still suffers from
OL,8,Fchronic pain in several parts of his
OL,9,Fbody
OL,11,FHe described how he often gets
OL,12,Fflashbacks, and when I asked him to
OL,13,Fdescribe them, he simply couldn't
OL,14,Fanswer what he sees or hears.
OL,16,FAsking him to describe what happened
OL,17,Fthat day was clearly too painful, and
OL,18,Fwhat was more important for him was to
OL,19,Fshare how his life has changed now and
OL,20,Fwhat he needs from Air India.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
