OL,7,FOn his behalf, Radd urged the company
OL,8,Fto provide more support for Vishwash
OL,9,Fand called for "the leadership team"
OL,10,Fto sit and "listen to his suffering".
OL,12,F"It isn't difficult advice to give (to
OL,13,FAir India). Go and meet - not your
OL,14,Fjunior people - the CEO, or the
OL,15,Fleadership team. Build an outreach
OL,16,Fprogramme.
