OL,7,F"He's the sole survivor. Sit with him
OL,8,Ffor half an hour and listen to his
OL,9,Fsuffering, and his family's suffering
OL,10,Fand then you can deploy your resources
OL,11,Faccordingly."
OL,13,FIn a statement, Air India said it is
OL,14,F"deeply conscious" of its
OL,15,F"responsibility to provide Mr Ramesh
OL,16,Fwith support through what must have
OL,17,Fbeen an unimaginable period".
