OL,7,FIt continued: "Care for him - and
OL,8,Findeed all families affected by the
OL,9,Ftragedy - remains our absolute
OL,10,Fpriority.
OL,12,F"Senior leaders from across Tata Group
OL,13,Fcontinue to visit families to express
OL,14,Ftheir deepest condolences.
OL,16,F"An offer has been made to Mr Ramesh's
OL,17,Frepresentatives to arrange such a
OL,18,Fmeeting, we will continue to reach out
OL,19,Fand we very much hope to receive a
OL,20,Fpositive response.
